\begin_inset Formula $-1$
\end_inset

, meaning that there is close to full crowding out.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Now consider the case where 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{u_{i}'}=0\forall i\in Contributors$
\end_inset

.
